  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">First Dedicated Elephant Nursery in South Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wildlife Conservation Trust (WCT) in conjunction with Hoedspruit Endangered Species Centre (HESC), have provided care and rehabilitation to orphaned elephants through the years.   During this time we have recognised the need to build a dedicated elephant orphanage on a separate piece of land.   This project was created to help us start raising funds to not only care for the current elephant orphan in the care at HESC, but most importantly to enable WCT to build a new dedicated orphanage.</narrative>
  </description>
